patterns.message:
❌ Wildcard icon imports are forbidden. Use named imports for better tree-shaking:

  BAD:  import * as Icons from 'lucide-react';
  GOOD: import { Play, Clock, Database } from 'lucide-react';

This prevents importing all 1000+ icons (~2.5MB) when you only need a few.
Run 'python3 scripts/fix_wildcard_imports.py' to auto-fix.

paths.message:
❌ Import specific icons from lucide-react instead of using wildcard imports.

  BAD:  import * as Icons from 'lucide-react';
  GOOD: import { Play, Clock, Database } from 'lucide-react';

❌ Import specific icons from @mui/icons-material instead of using wildcard imports.

  BAD:  import * as MuiIcons from '@mui/icons-material';
  GOOD: import { Add, Delete, Edit } from '@mui/icons-material';
